Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.33,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:14.94,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.78,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:32.36,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.35,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.77,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}Mister. I don't know what's going on, but don't you think you're a little unbecoming for an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.26,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:46.28,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Huh? That getup...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.91,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You're a State Alchemist, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.55,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,State Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.51,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:55.98,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't let you pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:01.39,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,That worked out perfectly, didn't it? Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:01.39,Serifa Std,,0,0,410,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:11.60,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22}{\fad(0,997)}Yeah... Now I’ve got a reason\Nto beat the crap out of you.
